        <h2>Our Safety Management System</h2>
        <p>Acme Chemicals operates under a comprehensive Safety Management System certified to ISO 45001:2018 — the international standard for occupational health and safety. Our global lost-time incident rate (LTIR) is consistently below 0.15, approximately 10x better than the chemical industry average.</p>
        <p>We conduct quarterly Process Hazard Analyses at all production facilities, mandatory near-miss reporting, and monthly safety walks involving senior leadership.</p>
        <ul class="check-list">
          <li>ISO 45001:2018 certified across all plants</li>
          <li>LTIR: 0.14 (vs. industry average 1.4)</li>
          <li>OSHA VPP Star status at US facilities</li>
          <li>Responsible Care® signatory</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
